  reward_weights:
    coverage: 0.3          # Â±50% allowed
    route_length: -0.1     # Â±50% allowed
    travel_time: -0.2      # Â±50% allowed
    transfers: -0.15       # Â±50% allowed
    demand_served: 0.2     # Â±50% allowed
    emissions: -0.1        # Â±50% allowed
  coverage_threshold: 0.7
  emission_limit: 1000
```

**Validation Logic Example:**  
```python
# src/utils/feature_encoder.py
def _validate_route(route: List[int]):
    coverage_ratio = len(set(route)) / total_stops
    if coverage_ratio < coverage_threshold:
        raise ConstraintViolation("Coverage threshold violated")
```

